[{"id":"VH942116","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><include href=\"../Passage/VH942113.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">¿Qué idea común de la época se comunica con el lenguaje contrastante de la última estrofa del poema?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH942116_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<div class=\"stimulus_reference\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"poetry style:1\"><div class=\"title\"><p class=\"title_line passage-title\">CXCI</p></div><div class=\"verse\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_1\"></span>Es la mujer del hombre lo más bueno,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>y locura decir que lo más malo,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>su vida suele ser y su regalo,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>su muerte suele ser y su veneno.</span><br/></div><div class=\"verse\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">5</span><span class=\"indent indent_1\"></span>Cielo a los ojos cándido y sereno,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>que muchas veces al infierno igualo,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>por raro al mundo su valor señalo</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>por falso al hombre su rigor condeno.</span><br/></div><div class=\"verse\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_1\"></span><span class=\"focus_start focus_id:VH942113_1 itemref:VH942119\" id=\"VH942113_1\"></span>Ella nos da su sangre, ella nos cría<span class=\"focus_end focus_idref:VH942113_1\"></span>,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">10</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>no ha hecho el cielo cosa más ingrata;</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>es un ángel, y a veces una harpía<span class=\"footnote\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"footnote_mark\">1</span><span class=\"footnote_text\">harpía: arpía, bruja</span></span>;</span><br/></div><div class=\"verse\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>quiere, aborrece, trata bien, maltrata,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>y es la mujer, al fin, como sangría<span class=\"footnote\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"footnote_mark\">2</span><span class=\"footnote_text\">sangría: práctica médica antigua en que se hacían incisiones en el cuerpo para curar las enfermedades</span></span>,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>que a veces da salud y a veces mata.</span><br/></div><span class=\"mandatory_credit_block\"><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\">Félix Lope de Vega</span><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic\">Las literaturas hispánicas: España</span></span><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\">Detroit: Wayne State University Press, 1991.</span><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\">(Se publicó originalmente en <span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic\">Rimas humanas</span> en 1602).</span></span></div></div></div>"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Los sentimientos ambivalentes hacia la mujer</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">El valor científico de la medicina</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">El miedo existencial a la muerte</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Las diferencias entre el hombre y la mujer</p>"],"answer":0}]